ress for $500 or $5000 to wear once they are now renting it for $50 or $500 instead, from other women on the platform.\r\n\r\n10,000 women visit Style Lend on a monthly basis to rent fashion items but to also lend fashion from their closet. They submit items, we approve them and they ship to our warehouse where we process the items, photograph, list and store for free.\r\n\r\nWe then rent them out to customers on Style Lend and split the profit 50/50 with the lenders (owners of the items)\r\n\r\nInvestors include Estee Lauder Family, Y combinator, DeNA, Social Starts, Metamorphic Ventures, Structure Capital etc.\r\n\r\nStyle Lend is looking for a Social Media Intern who is excellent at creating and managing content. Style Lend has the world\'s biggest closet with 2500 items so you would have the best selection of designer fashion to shoot for Instagram, fb, snapchat and other social channels.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for an excellent eye for fashion and style and a problem solver with a great attitude to join our startup for the spring of 2018. Our intern will have the chance to work with our Ecommerce and Digital/Social departments in order to understand the full Style Lend online experience.\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\nWhat youll do:\r\n\r\n Write engaging articles about fashion.\r\n\r\n Gather data about fashion industry and report on them in the form of blogging.\r\n\r\n Link Style Lend fashion items to your stories.\r\n\r\n Write about the Style Lend community\r\n\r\n Find opportunities to insert Style Lend into culturally-relevant events\r\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\r\nWho you are:\r\n\r\n Friendly, patient and quick-thinking\r\n\r\n Strong communication skills\r\n\r\n A keen eye for detail, fashion, style\r\n\r\n Well-presented, polite and tactful\r\n\r\n Can handle customers in a calm manner\r\n\r\n A willingness and ability to listen to and follow instructions\r\n\r\n A team player\r\n\r\n Ability and willingness to interface with all levels and departments within the company\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:43:\"Blogging/Content Creation Intern @StyleLend\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:41:\"bloggingcontent-creation-intern-stylelend\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:18:41\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:18:41\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:57:\"http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=2005\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:7:\"noo_job\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:5;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:2004;s:11:\"post_author\";s:2:\"30\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:2771:\"<h2>Description</h2>\r\nStyle Lend is the new way women are dressing for events. Instead of buying a new dress for $500 or $5000 to wear once they are now renting it for $50 or $500 instead, from other women on the platform.\r\n\r\n10,000 women visit Style Lend on a monthly basis to rent fashion items but to also lend fashion from their closet. They submit items, we approve them and they ship to our warehouse where we process the items, photograph, list and store for free.\r\n\r\nWe then rent them out to customers on Style Lend and split the profit 50/50 with the lenders (owners of the items)\r\n\r\nInvestors include Estee Lauder Family, Y combinator, DeNA, Social Starts, Metamorphic Ventures, Structure Capital etc.\r\n\r\nStyle Lend is looking for a Social Media Intern who is excellent at creating and managing content. Style Lend has the world\'s biggest closet with 2500 items so you would have the best selection of designer fashion to shoot for Instagram, fb, snapchat and other social channels.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for an excellent eye for fashion and style and a problem solver with a great attitude to join our startup for the spring of 2018. Our intern will have the chance to work with our Ecommerce and Digital/Social departments in order to understand the full Style Lend online experience.\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\nWhat youll do:\r\n\r\n Assist in conceptualizing cool/engaging/fun content\r\n\r\n Create and execute the shoot for the content\r\n\r\n Edit content to get ready for posting\r\n\r\n Post and manage comments and engagement of content\r\n\r\n Create content calendar with help of Chief Marketing Officer\r\n\r\n Shoot content with IPhone\r\n\r\n Discover influencers to collaborate with for content\r\n\r\n Add/update new products on the website, product merchandising &amp; inventory analysis\r\n\r\n Assist team with Q&amp;A of websites across devices, browsers, portals and social properties\r\n\r\n Conduct market research and competitive analysis; research new and developing trends and technologies as it pertains to Social Media and Ecommerce\r\n\r\n Pull and analyze weekly/monthly analytics of social performance\r\n\r\n Find opportunities to insert Style Lend into culturally-relevant events\r\n\r\n Work closely with creative team assisting with any photo-shoots to capture social media and other organizational tasks\r\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\r\nWho you are:\r\n\r\n Friendly, patient and quick-thinking\r\n\r\n Strong communication skills\r\n\r\n A keen eye for detail, fashion, style\r\n\r\n Well-presented, polite and tactful\r\n\r\n Can handle customers in a calm manner\r\n\r\n A willingness and ability to listen to and follow instructions\r\n\r\n A team player\r\n\r\n Ability and willingness to interface with all levels and departments within the company\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:30:\"Social Media Intern @StyleLend\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_stat