mment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:7;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:2000;s:11:\"post_author\";s:2:\"30\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:2192:\"<h2>Description</h2>\r\nStyle Lend is the new way women are dressing for events. Instead of buying a new dress for $500 or $5000 to wear once they are now renting it for $50 or $500 instead, from other women on the platform.\r\n\r\n10,000 women visit Style Lend on a monthly basis to rent fashion items but to also lend fashion from their closet. They submit items, we approve them and they ship to our warehouse where we process the items, photograph, list and store for free.\r\n\r\nWe then rent them out to customers on Style Lend and split the profit 50/50 with the lenders (owners of the items)\r\n\r\nInvestors include Estee Lauder Family, Y combinator, DeNA, Social Starts, Metamorphic Ventures, Structure Capital etc.\r\n\r\nStyle Lend is looking for a Social Media Intern who is excellent at creating and managing content. Style Lend has the world\'s biggest closet with 2500 items so you would have the best selection of designer fashion to shoot for Instagram, fb, snapchat and other social channels.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for an excellent eye for fashion and style and a problem solver with a great attitude to join our startup for the spring of 2018. Our intern will have the chance to work with our Ecommerce and Digital/Social departments in order to understand the full Style Lend online experience.\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\nWhat youll do:\r\n\r\n Assist in customer engagement.\r\n\r\n Answer questions that have to do with styling from customers.\r\n\r\n Learn about orders and inquiries\r\n\r\n Add/update new products on the website, product merchandising &amp; inventory analysis\r\n\r\n Assist team with Q&amp;A of websites across devices, browsers, portals and social properties\r\n\r\n Find opportunities to insert Style Lend into culturally-relevant events\r\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\r\nWho you are:\r\n\r\n Friendly, patient and quick-thinking\r\n\r\n Strong communication skills\r\n\r\n A keen eye for detail, fashion, style\r\n\r\n Well-presented, polite and tactful\r\n\r\n Can handle customers in a calm manner\r\n\r\n A willingness and ability to listen to and follow instructions\r\n\r\n A team player\r\n\r\n Ability and willingness to interface with all levels and departments within the company\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:34:\"Customer Service Intern @StyleLend\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:33:\"customer-service-intern-stylelend\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:20:28\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:20:28\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:57:\"http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=2000\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:7:\"noo_job\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:8;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:1998;s:11:\"post_author\";s:2:\"30\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:2462:\"<h2>Description</h2>\r\nAt NJ Business Associates, we believe the success of a company is in direct correlation with the success of its workforce. We value integrity and work ethic as we believe they are imperative instruments in the evolution of a thriving company. We are offering internships for our Client Relations Representative position.\r\n\r\nDue to our success and unprecedented growth, we have opened up a few positions in our sales and marketing department. We are seeking qualified professionals that would like to take their \"Winning Mindsets\" and apply them to lucrative business internships.\r\n\r\nWhat NJ Business Associates offers:\r\n\r\n Extensive training in all areas of sales, marketing, and management\r\n\r\n Advancement is based on promotion/merit\r\n\r\n Development of leadership and communication\r\n\r\n Positive work environment\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\nResponsibilities include (but not limited to):\r\n\r\nAttending team meetings\r\n\r\nAccount Management\r\n\r\nCustomer Acquisition\r\n\r\nOne to one sales based interaction with customers\r\n\r\nCustomer Service\r\n\r\nMaintain relationships with customers, clients, and partners\r\n\r\nQualifications:\r\n\r\nSales, marketing, customer service, and/or retail experience preferred\r\n\r\nIndividuals that can work as part of a team as well as independently\r\n\r\nProfessional image\r\n\r\nStrong communication skills (written and verbal)\r\n\r\n*We are willing to train highly motivated people for full-time management, customer service, marketing and sales opportunities.*\r\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\r\nThis is an outstanding opportunity for recent college grads or those looking to make a change in their careers to a more stable position with greater advancement opportunity. Internships are available for qualified students. We will be responding to your resume immediately if selected for an interview. We apologize, but we can only contact those we select to meet in person.\r\n\r\nJob Requirements\r\n\r\nIdeal candidates have an uncommon combination of attributes. They are self-motivated, entrepreneurial individuals who are ready to leave behind the constraints of the traditional corporate job model and build a secure future of their own.\r\n\r\n Must possess excellent interpersonal communication skills\r\n\r\n Maintain a high level of professionalism &amp; integrity\r\n\r\n Experience with public speaking for presenting to groups\r\n\r\n Demonstrated leadership ability\r\n\r\n Demonstrated critical thinking and problem-solving skills\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:54:\"Paid Internship - Gain real life business experience -\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:50:\"paid-internship-gain-real-life-business-experience\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:14:30\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:14:30\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:57:\"http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=1998\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:7:\"noo_job\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:9;O:7:\"WP_Post\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:1996;s:11:\"post_author\";s:2:\"30\";s:9:\"post_date\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:13:\"post_date_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-13 00:00:00\";s:12:\"post_content\";s:3021:\"<h2>Description</h2>\r\nAll qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, religion, national origin, disability, veteran status, age, marital status, pregnancy, genetic information, or other legally protected status.\r\n\r\nInformation Technology Intern - IT Applications\r\n\r\n203520-868\r\n\r\nCompany Overview\r\n\r\nPSAV is a leading provider in the audiovisual and event experiences industry delivering creative production, advanced technology and staging to help our customers deliver more dynamic and impactful experiences at their meetings, trade shows and special events. As the provider of choice at more than 1,500 leading hotels, resorts and convention centers throughout the U.S., Canada, the Caribbean, Mexico, Europe and the Middle East, PSAVs customers comprise event organizers, corporations, trade associations and meeting planners. Our customers choose PSAV for its innovative and comprehensive service offerings, as well as our exceptional customer service from more than 9,000 highly trained staff across a global platform.\r\n\r\nPosition Overview\r\n\r\nAssist the Applications Development Group in enhancing and supporting PSAV applications. You will be hands on extending and upgrading the existing web-based code, evaluating database query improvements, upgrading mobile applications and writing new reports.\r\n\r\nThis position is based in Rosemont, IL. Temporary housing is not provided for this role.\r\n\r\nKey Job Responsibilities\r\n\r\n Working under the supervision of a Senior Developer, you will design, develop, and test system features using PSAVs software development methodology.\r\n\r\n Working with the Project Management Office, you will evaluate and document feature requests, bug fixes, build a plan for project delivery, with an ultimate goal of user acceptance.\r\n\r\n Working with the Application Services team you will package and release you system changes as required by our Environment Change Management process.\r\n\r\nJob Qualifications\r\n\r\n Currently enrolled in a Bachelors program at least to the sophomore level at an accredited college or university\r\n\r\n Experience programming with C# or VB.Net\r\n\r\n Experience programming with ASP.Net and client/server architecture desired\r\n\r\n Experience working with JavaScript, JavaScript libraries and frameworks\r\n\r\n Experience writing T-SQL syntax in a Microsoft SQL Server environment\r\n\r\n The ability to work in an agile and creative environment\r\n\r\n Solid communication and customer service skills\r\n\r\n Highly motivated individual with passion for customer service, follow-through and learning\r\n\r\nCompetencies\r\n\r\n Exceed Customer Expectations\r\n\r\n Teamwork\r\n\r\n Communication skills\r\n\r\n#LI-KS2\r\n\r\nPSAV123\r\n\r\nRosemont, Illinois, United States\r\n\r\nIntern\r\n\r\nApply Here:\r\n<a href=\"http://www.click2apply.net/mqgtv5b46kcwv7hc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">http://www.Click2Apply.net/mqgtv5b46kcwv7hc</a>\r\n\r\nPI102003188\r\n\r\nnullnull\";s:10:\"post_title\";s:47:\"Information Technology Intern - IT Applications\";s:12:\"post_excerpt\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:14:\"comment_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:13:\"post_password\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"post_name\";s:45:\"information-technology-intern-it-applications\";s:7:\"to_ping\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"pinged\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"post_modified\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:15:40\";s:17:\"post_modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2018-04-15 13:15:40\";s:21:\"post_content_filtered\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"post_parent\";i:0;s:4:\"guid\";s:57:\"http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=1996\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"post_type\";s:7:\"noo_job\";s:14:\"post_mime_type\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"comment_count\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:10:\"post_count\";i:10;s:12:\"current_post\";i:-1;s:11:\"in_the_loop\";b:0;s:4:\"post\";r:93;s:13:\"comment_count\";i:0;s:15:\"current_comment\";i:-1;s:11:\"found_posts\";s:3:\"251\";s:13:\"max_num_pages\";d:26;s:21:\"max_num_comment_pages\";i:0;s:9:\"is_single\";b:0;s:10:\"is_preview\";b:0;s:7:\"is_page\";b:0;s:10:\"is_archive\";b:1;s:7:\"is_date\";b:0;s:7:\"is_year\";b:0;s:8:\"is_month\";b:0;s:6:\"is_day\";b:0;s:7:\"is_time\";b:0;s:9:\"is_author\";b:0;s:11:\"is_category\";b:0;s:6:\"is_tag\";b:0;s:6:\"is_tax\";b:0;s:9:\"is_search\";b:1;s:7:\"is_feed\";b:0;s:15:\"is_comment_feed\";b:0;s:12:\"is_trackback\";b:0;s:7:\"is_home\";b:0;s:6:\"is_404\";b:0;s:8:\"is_embed\";b:0;s:8:\"is_paged\";b:0;s:8:\"is_admin\";b:1;s:13:\"is_attachment\";b:0;s:11:\"is_singular\";b:0;s:9:\"is_robots\";b:0;s:13:\"is_posts_page\";b:0;s:20:\"is_post_type_archive\";b:1;s:25:\"\0WP_Query\0query_vars_hash\";s:32:\"be89ccaf265534a7ed777b8adbde5d55\";s:28:\"\0WP_Query\0query_vars_changed\";b:0;s:17:\"thumbnails_cached\";b:0;s:19:\"\0WP_Query\0stopwords\";N;s:23:\"\0WP_Query\0compat_fields\";a:2:{i:0;s:15:\"query_vars_hash\";i