riting and computer skills, experience in writing business plans a plus.\r\n\r\n- Superior verbal communication, presentation skills, and customer service.\r\n\r\n- Credit can be arranged for current students.\r\n\r\n- Strong organizational skills and the ability to multi-task.\r\n\r\n- Ability to work well independently as well as in a team environment.\r\n\r\n- Analytical thinking capability.\r\n\r\n- Ability to translate business requirements to technical specifications and needs.\r\n\r\nMinimum duration 2 months','Communications Liaison','','publish','closed','closed','','communications-liaison','','','2018-04-15 13:26:04','2018-04-15 13:26:04','',0,'http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=2015',0,'noo_job','',0),(2016,30,'1970-01-01 08:00:00','1970-01-01 08:00:00','Test Prep San Francisco','Test Prep San Francisco','','publish','closed','closed','','test-prep-san-francisco','','','1970-01-01 08:00:00','1970-01-01 08:00:00','',0,'',0,'noo_company','',0),(2017,30,'2018-04-12 00:00:00','2018-04-12 00:00:00','<h2>Description</h2>\r\nWe are a full service education company disrupting the space by combining holistic and mindful modalities with academic study an test preparation. With offices based in NYC and The Bay Area, we\'re seeking emerging and thoughtful interns who would like to create videos, take photos, an help develop online program(s) video and photos for a new project we\'re working on.\r\n\r\nMinimum duration: 2 months\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\n- Assist in all aspects of video and photographic communications and contribute to planning and storyboarding\r\n\r\n- Assist in the end-to-end process from storyboarding to logistics to shooting to editing and publishing\r\n\r\n- Film video and shoot photographs in local environment (New York and San Francisco)\r\n\r\n- Record desktop computer screens and actions for demo and training videos\r\n\r\n- Use existing original and stock footage to produce new videos\r\n\r\n- Contribute to mixing an