le Drive\r\n\r\n Ability to multitask\r\n\r\n Knowledge of label and current artists\r\n\r\nPlease send cover letter and resume to evan@dominorecordco.com','Publicity Intern','','publish','closed','closed','','publicity-intern','','','2018-04-15 14:55:21','2018-04-15 14:55:21','',0,'http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=2084',0,'noo_job','',0),(2085,30,'1970-01-01 08:00:00','1970-01-01 08:00:00','Domino Recording Company','Domino Recording Company','','publish','closed','closed','','domino-recording-company','','','1970-01-01 08:00:00','1970-01-01 08:00:00','',0,'',0,'noo_company','',0),(2086,30,'2018-04-12 00:00:00','2018-04-12 00:00:00','<h2>Description</h2>\r\nGeneral Description:\r\n\r\nABCDs Planning and Grants Department is looking for an Intern to provide assistance with data collection and analysis in support of the agencys Strategic Planning and community needs assessment efforts. The Intern will assist in a broad variety of data collection, analysis, reporting, and program development.\r\n\r\nTo Apply: Please complete our Online Application at\r\n<a href=\"https://www.volgistics.com/ex/portal.dll/ap?ap=1825256508\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.volgistics.com/ex/portal.dll/ap?ap=1825256508</a>.\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\nDuties/Responsibilities:\r\n\r\nIdentify and access secondary source data sources\r\n\r\nAssist with primary source data collection and validation\r\n\r\nAssist with the development of survey instruments, focus group questionnaires, and key informant interview scripts\r\n\r\nProduce visualized gathered data\r\n\r\nProduce status update memorandum\r\n\r\nMaintain team project site\r\n\r\nAssist with planning, coordination and implementation of strategic planning events, including community meetings\r\n\r\nAssist with other related administrative tasks and projects as needed\r\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\r\nSkills &amp; Qualifications:\r\n\r\nStudents in a Masters level Urban or Public Policy, Sociolo