elop presentations to prospective partners \n<br />Create awareness of partners products and services through global social media channels \n<br />Utilize personal and team resources &amp; networks to identify additional partnership opportunities \n<br /> \n<br />Content Creation: \n<br />Develop compelling content and stories to be shared on Jetzy App and social media platforms \n<br />Work on promotion strategies, campaigns, press releases, etc. \n<br />Assist in building and sustaining the brand image through unique content \n<br />Share company message through various social outlets \n<br /> \n<br />Public Relations \n<br />Develop and contribute to public relations activities including publicity strategies, campaigns, press releases etc. \n<br />Create and list of relevant journalists, bloggers and influencers and proactively reach them to get the word out for Jetzy \n<br />Deal with inquiries from the public, the press, media and related organizations \n<br />Coordinate with news media as assigned, in development of appropriate news stories \n<br />Maintain tracking report of public relations activitynull','Marketing Trainee/Intern','','publish','closed','closed','','marketing-traineeintern','','','2018-04-12 00:00:00','2018-04-12 00:00:00','',0,'http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=2191',0,'noo_job','',0),(2192,1,'2018-04-13 15:30:43','2018-04-13 15:30:43','','xdf','','inherit','open','closed','','xdf','','','2018-04-13 15:30:43','2018-04-13 15:30:43','',0,'http://ec2-184-73-133-229.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/xdf.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(2193,30,'2018-04-12 00:00:00','2018-04-12 00:00:00','<h2>Description</h2> Come work with us at Spencer\'s &amp; Spirit Halloween, where youll be working with the best and brightest colleagues as you help us deliver the most fun experience and product possible to our guests. Were fast-paced and take our work seriously, but we always have a good laugh at the end of the day. Wal